Solution: 
- Add effective_date to the price list;
- Add "effective priority" to reorder features;
- Clearly display "reference source + effective period" on the UI.

Acceptance criteria set first:
- Macro-average F1 ≥ 0.75;
- P95 latency per request ≤ 80ms;
- Default confidence threshold 0.55;
- Trigger alerts for anger/frustration.

I will clarify the types of memory again:
- Preferences (e.g., "likes comparison tables");
- Taboos (e.g., "don't call before 9 AM");
- Commitments ("provide a quote next week");
- Contacts/Roles;
- Budget range;
- Industry characteristics.
